<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Accessibility
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    SVG charts render the root SVG with an accessible role and label by default. Use <Code>Role</Code>, <Code>AriaLabel</Code>, <Code>AccessibilityTitle</Code>, <Code>AccessibilityDescription</Code>, and <Code>TabIndex</Code> when a chart needs custom assistive text or keyboard focus.
</DocsPageParagraph>

